Puso Ni Comi:
An anime adaptation of Sega's Phantasy Star Online 2 game's official web manga Puso Ni Comi: Phantasy Star Online 2 Comic. The story follows the lax, less than weighty daily life of the ARKS force members. 

(Source: ANN)
